Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.92,0:22:39.09,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}哭泣時  氣餒時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.67,0:22:43.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}時はシンプルな思考でTry Again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.67,0:22:43.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}就要簡單地思考後Try Again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.39,0:22:47.68,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}弾まない足取り止めて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.39,0:22:47.68,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}苦惱地停在原地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.77,0:22:50.48,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}胸いっぱいに深呼吸しよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.77,0:22:50.48,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}這時就放輕鬆地深呼吸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.73,0:22:54.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}伸べた手で優しく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.73,0:22:54.06,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}溫柔地伸出雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:22:57.65,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}触れる未来の予感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:22:57.65,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}似乎能夠到未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:23:00.99,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}暖かい眼差しと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:23:00.99,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}堅定有力的視線
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:04.37,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}向き合えるよ　一緒なら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:04.37,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}和你一起的話  一定可以
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.45,0:23:06.91,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll show you a wonderful world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.45,0:23:06.91,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll show you a wonderful world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.95,0:23:10.71,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I came to show you a good time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.95,0:23:10.71,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I came to show you a good time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.50,0:23:15.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}言葉だけじゃ足りないみたいだから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.50,0:23:15.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}有些事僅憑言語無法表達清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.71,0:23:19.59,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}目を離さないで　いつもFace to Face
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.71,0:23:19.59,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}那就不要離開我的視野  永遠Face to Face
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.63,0:23:31.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}躓いても　笑いながら君と歩いて行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.63,0:23:31.06,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}就算遇到困難 也能笑著和你一同前行
